      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 16:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔强调降息理由，美元下跌 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/dovish-powell-adds-fuel-to-dollar-s-longest-plunge-in-16-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席鲍威尔确认央行下个月将降息的预期后，美元暴跌，降低了美国固定收益资产的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/dovish-powell-adds-fuel-to-dollar-s-longest-plunge-in-16-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:44:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔谈降息，全球股市创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/global-stocks-head-for-a-record-high-as-powell-talks-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国即将降息且没有出现衰退信号，投资者信心增强，全球股市在收复本月早些时候动荡造成的损失后创下了历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/global-stocks-head-for-a-record-high-as-powell-talks-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:41:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Topgolf 评级被下调至卖出，因担心分拆“为时已晚”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/topgolf-modg-hit-by-double-downgrade-on-fear-spinoff-comes-too-late</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Topgolf Callaway Brands Corp. 同名练习场的销售放缓以及沉重的债务负担有可能吓跑买家，促使雷蒙詹姆斯 (Raymond James) 大幅下调了该公司的评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/topgolf-modg-hit-by-double-downgrade-on-fear-spinoff-comes-too-late</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:19:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔“确定”9 月降息，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市全线上涨，债券收益率下跌，杰罗姆·鲍威尔发出迄今为止最明确的信号，美联储将于 9 月开始降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 22:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
